settings.text: I bought a Titan Power+ cable as a result of solid research and out of desperation. I have an autistic son who has managed to damage every cable he’s ever had. It has been subjected to some harsh treatment by him and has come out unscathed. Would I buy another? Yes. Would I recommend them? Undoubtedly!

settings.text: The one thing I love the most: reversible USB plugs! Why haven’t we had these before? I don't have to mess around trying to plug it in when it simply slots in the plug both ways. settings.text: I have bought a few of each of these cables so I did not have to constantly move them around. I alsokeep an extra cable in the car to hook up to my car system and charge my phone when I forget to. I have found their products quite impressive and I will definitely be buying more from them.

settings.text: The cable is crazy strong. My dog is no match for this baby,. My favorite thing about this cable is the green light. You can always find this in the darkness. settings.text: Through continuous innovation and listening to our customers, we've transformed our charging cable into the pinnacle of reliability and convenience for your daily needs

settings.accordion_question: Just How Durable Is This Cable?
settings.accordion_answer: The Titan FastTech Cable takes durability to ludicrous new heights. Engineered with ultra-reinforced construction and premium materials, it's virtually indestructible. We've torture-tested this beast to withstand over 25,000 bend cycles. It's built to outlast and outlive.

Yes, every FastTech purchase includes our innovative MagSnap magnetic cable management system. With a satisfying snap, the cable effortlessly attaches/detaches to eliminate clutter, prevent tangling, and allow for compact cable control at your fingertips.

Does it ever! Powered by HyperConduct wiring and a monstrously powerful 120W output, the FastTech provides hyper-charging at blistering speeds up to 8X faster than standard cables. It will take you from 0 to 50% battery in just 20 minutes flat.

settings.accordion_question: Does it really have Led lights integrated with it?
settings.accordion_answer: The Titan FastTech Cable features our groundbreaking LumiCore illumination technology. Integrated LED lighting pulses along the cable's length with a mesmerizing luminous glow. It's an unmistakable signature design that allows you to easily locate the cable in dimly lit spaces. But it also just looks insanely cool, putting your hyper-charged power on display.

settings.accordion_question: Can I Use It To Charge My Laptop?
settings.accordion_answer: Absolutely! While many charging cables are underpowered for laptops, the Titan FastTech Cable is a heavy-duty USB-C powerhouse rated for up to 120W. That gives you the juice to quickly and safely charge even the most power-hungry laptops and notebooks. Whether a featherweight MacBook or bulky gaming beast, this hyper-cable will get your portable workstation powered up at ludicrous speeds while you're on the move.

settings.accordion_question: What Devices Can I Use It With?
settings.accordion_answer: This cable is a true universal powerhouse compatible with any device - phones, laptops, tablets, gaming consoles, you name it. Whether Android, iOS, Windows or otherwise, the FastTech charges them all. It's the one hyper-cable to rule all your gear.

We stand behind the FastTech's indestructible build quality with an unlimited lifetime warranty. If anything ever happens, we'll replace your cable free of charge - no questions asked. Intentional abuse or misuse isn't covered, but any reasonable wear, defects or unexpected failures are 100% covered for life.

settings.accordion_question: Is It Safe For My Devices?
settings.accordion_answer: Absolutely. The integrated SafeCore chip constantly monitors temperature and current to prevent overheating, overcharging or any battery damage. You can charge overnight without worry, as it intelligently protects your gear from potential hazards.

This cable laughs at fraying and bending issues thanks to its ultra-reinforced design from end-to-end. The metal-reinforced connector tips can withstand over 1,500lbs of force. And the angular MagSnap magnetic connectors eliminate strain from awkward cable bends.

settings.accordion_question: Can I Use It With Power Banks/Car Chargers?
settings.accordion_answer: You bet. The FastTech Cable seamlessly integrates with power banks, car chargers, and any other charging accessories you may have. Its universal compatibility ensures it plays nicely with all your gear.

Not sure about investing in a Titan Product? Take advantage of our 30-day return policy. If you're not completely satisfied with your purchase for any reason, simply return it within 30 days for a full refund. No hassle, no questions asked.

Rest assured, your Titan Smart Cable is backed by our lifetime warranty. In the rare event your Titan product encounters any faults or breaks through no fault of yours, we'll provide a free replacement.
